product.name: WENNEBIRD Superior Carpet Floor Mats for 2021-2025 Chevrolet Suburban 7 Seater (Not for 8 Seater), 0.6 Inch Thickness Rugs, Premium All Weather Anti-Slip Waterproof Floor Liners - 4pc
product.description:
WENNEBIRD Superior Carpet Floor Mats, providing ultimate comfort and protection.
These carefully selected soft and plush (0.6 in thick) carpets provide ultimate comfort, have fasteners matching the car's standard fasteners that make a secure fit. Cleaning and installation are a breeze, courtesy of the TPE waterproof layer and custom design.
Elevate your driving experience with the superior of style, comfort, and protection for WENNEBIRD floor mats.
High-quality plush needle plush polypropylene carpet, thickness up to 0.6 inches (1.52 cm), feet feel soft and comfortable and will help dampen noise inside the vehicle.
The driver side floor mat is designed with a heel pad, and the additional pedal is integrated with the floor mat using a hot-melt process, which ensure driving safety while also improving driving comfort.
The WENNEBIRD carpet floor mats have fasteners matching the car's standard fasteners that make installation fast and secure.
The backing layer is WENNEBIRD's innovation “Friction Claws” backing material, by increasing friction with the car floor, our floor mats provide a secure fit without Velcro and without causing damage to the floors.
The meticulous leather hemming sewing process can protect the edge and of the floor mat, and the zinc alloy buckle protects the seam of the leather edging. The floor mats look complete and sophisticated.
Utilizing advanced heat pressing technology, we skillfully fuse the TPE waterproof layer between the plush carpet and "Friction Claw" backing, ensuring excellent waterproofing and non-slip functionality.
The driver side floor mat is designed with a heel pad and extended to the left footrest area, which to ensure driving safety while also improving driving comfort.
The passenger side floor mat is full coverage designed and a luxurious, plush feel that allows you to even experience it barefoot.
Enjoy unparalleled soft and comfort.
The 2nd row floor mat is full coverage designed and a luxurious, plush feel that allows you to even experience it barefoot.
In this Install Instructions video, we walk you through the step-by-step process of installing your WENNEBIRD floor mats with ease and precision.
Know how to fit the mats perfectly into your vehicle, ensuring an exact and seamless installation.
In this cleaning methods video, know how to high efficiently or deep cleaning methods to ensuring easy maintenance and preserve the mats' premium quality.
How do these mats attach to the car floor?
The WENNEBIRD carpet floor mats have fasteners matching the car's standard fasteners that make installation, and the backing layer adopts a partial Velcro, effectively preventing the floor mats from moving.
These carpet floor mats easy to clean and install?
You can use a vacuum or water for cleaning. Additionally, we provide a video demonstrating the cleaning methods and installation process.
Can the zinc alloy logo on the floor mats be removed?
Yes, you can easily remove the zinc alloy logo from the back of the floor mats using a Phillips screwdriver.
product.bullet_points:
• Perfect Fit: Custom for 2021-2025 Chevrolet Suburban 7 Seater, not fit 8 Seater. Compared to OEM and universal mats, it offers maximum floor protection. The driver’s side floor mat is designed with a unique anti-slip texture heel pad, which ensure driving safety while also improving comfort. The mats feature a leather hemming sewing process that seamlessly integrates with the interior, giving them an elegant and modern texture.
• Multilayer Structure: The rugs feature an impressive 0.6-in thickness, and made of three layers combined by hot press technology. The first layer of premium plush carpet helps reduce interior car noise and delivers outstanding comfort and support; Second layer is TPE, allowing it can be flame retardant and waterproof; Backing layer is original “Friction Claws” material, by increasing the friction on backing with car floor, keeps mats from moving without damaging floors.
• All Weather Protection: WENNEBIRD floor rugs are designed to provide complete automotive floor protection from water, dirt, mud, salt, rain, snow. The thick carpet material has anti-slip characteristics that other floor mats do not have in rainy and snowy weather. The TPE waterproof layer ensures that water doesn't seep onto the vehicle floor, keeping it clean and dry in all seasons.
• Easy Clean and Quick Install: WENNEBIRD carpet floor mats have fasteners matching the car's standard fasteners that make installation fast and secure. While being just as easy to clean. Simply remove them from your vehicle, rinse with water and dry, or use a vacuum cleaner to remove dirt and debris. Make your floor mats new again.
• Certified Safe Materials: In our commitment to providing you with high-quality items, all WENNEBIRD floor mats are made from SGS certified materials that are non-toxic and odorless, eliminating any unpleasant rubber smell.
